name: FARSGUL #11
description:
When an alien virus infected the world humans and machines bonded. We escaped into the virtual world to fight for our existence. This is new URTH an original series featuring an array of original characters. FARSGUL is a twisted creation of Demon Ox. Three tortured souls were combined into a horrific nightmare come alive.

By holding a character from this series you will be eligible for secret drops into your wallet. Collect all of the characters for chances to receive the entire comic when it is released. All characters are copyright @smileghostnft follow me on Twitter.
